rtunities. At Breach Secure Now, you will find opportunities to grow as a professional, develop new skills, and gain experience in the rapidly growing cybersecurity industry.We offer competitive compensation and benefits, including health, dental & vision insurance, 401K plan with company matching, PTO & paid holidays. Breach Secure Now is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all team members.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/job-apply/4066737732', 135, 1);
