INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (166, 'SQL Developer', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-08 19:24:30', 'LISTED', 'About Us: Join a Fortune 500 company that has been voted one of the top places to work for large companies. We are embarking on an exciting cloud migration project and are looking for a talented SQL Developer to join our dynamic team. Project Details: You will be part of a critical cloud migration project, focusing on automating tasks and ensuring seamless integration of provider surveys into our application. This role is pivotal in enhancing user experience and operational efficiency. Day-to-Day Responsibilities:Program automation of tasks and ensure error messages are user-friendly.Collaborate with providers to schedule surveys through the application or via text.Work within a drag-and-drop landscape, similar to Visio, to create SQL-based protocols.Rapidly learn and visualize a wide network of different systems and processes. What We’re Looking For:Must-Have Technologies/Experience:Strong SQL experience and the ability to read complex SQL code.Experience with Requirement GatheringExcellent soft skills: eager to learn, quick to adapt, and sharp. Nice-to-Haves:Experience with Oracle.EDI experience.Web development experience.Healthcare or pharmaceutical industry experience. Why Join Us?Be part of a Fortune 25 company.Work in an environment recognized as one of the top places to work for large companies.Engage in a significant cloud migration project that will enhance your skills and career. Apply Now: If you are a motivated SQL Developer looking to make an impact in a leading company, we want to hear from you! Apply today and be part of our innovative team.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/job-apply/4068505219', 56, 1);
INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (167, 'Senior Python Developer with Big Data Platform', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-08 17:29:28', 'LISTED', 'About US: We are a company that provides innovative, transformative IT services and solutions. We are passionate about helping our clients achieve their goals and exceed their expectations. We strive to provide the best possible experience for our clients and employees. We are committed to continuous improvement and innovation, and we are always looking for ways to improve our services and solutions. We believe in working collaboratively with our clients and employees to achieve success.  DS Technologies Inc is looking for Senior Python Developer with Big Data Platform role for one of our premier clients.  Job Title: Senior Python Developer with Big Data Platform  Location: 100% Remote  Industry: Telecommunications / IT Services  Job Category: Software Development, Big Data Engineering  Overview  Seeking a highly experienced Senior Python Developer with over 12 years of expertise in Big Data platforms. This role involves software development within a Big Data environment, utilizing tools like Python, Java, SQL, Linux, and AWS to support platform infrastructure for a long-term project with Teleworld/Comcast.  Position  Senior Python Developer (Software Development focus, Big Data Platform)  Responsibilities  Develop and maintain software solutions for a Big Data platform.Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure robust data processing and storage.Utilize Python (version 11), Java, SQL, Linux, and AWS to design, build, and optimize platform capabilities.Solve complex technical problems related to data processing, storage, and integration.  Requirement Qualifications  Minimum of 12+ years of relevant experience.Proficiency in Python (version 11).Strong experience in Java (any recent version).Solid knowledge of SQL and database management.Experience with Linux for environment configuration and handling.Familiarity with AWS cl