holders, driving project alignment and team collaboration.Familiar with the following technologies: Django, Docker, GitHub & GitHub Actions, AWS, DocuSign, React, Vue, Sentry, and other third-party integration solutions. ', 'https://www.linkedin.com/job-apply/4066859739', 121, 1);
