INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (175, 'Web Development Intern - Denver', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-11 10:38:35', 'LISTED', 'About Us  Business Web Solutions (BWS) was established in 2018 with a passionate team of Freelance Web Developers aiming to provide the most affordable web development and design services at the Lowest Price, tailored to small businesses, particularly those in tier-2 and tier-3 cities. BWS has its headquarters in USA and India and has a Global presence. We are a fast growing company so opportunities are more.  Job Description  We are looking for enthusiastic Web Development Interns to join our team. This flexible internship, with customizable durations of 1 to 6 months, offers remote work and is open to candidates who want to grow their skills in modern web technologies.  As a Web Development Intern, you''ll have the chance to contribute directly to live projects, gain practical experience in coding and design, and learn best practices in web development. You''ll work closely with experienced developers, enabling you to refine your skills and broaden your knowledge in a supportive environment.  Responsibilities:  Implement responsive web design principles to ensure websites are mobile-friendly and user-centric.Participate in project planning meetings and brainstorming sessions to support web development strategies.Collaborate with our design and development teams to optimize websites for speed, scalability, and SEO.Support troubleshooting and debugging processes to ensure website functionality.Learn and apply web development best practices, including clean coding, version control, and testing.   Requirements:  Basic knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript is a plus but not mandatory.Ability to work independently and effectively in a remote environment.A proactive attitude with a willingness to learn and adapt to new challenges.Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail.   Benefits:  Flexible internship duration: 1 to 6 months based on