INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (190, 'Web Developer', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-07 01:00:00', 'LISTED', 'We are hiring a Web Developer!  This position is responsible for taking designs and assets created by our Graphics department and using WordPress and Beaver Builder to develop them into fully functional and responsive homepages for client websites. Attention to detail and a solid understanding of CSS and responsive design are required. Previous experience with Beaver Builder is not required, though experience with it, or similar page builders, is beneficial.***  We, at BxB Media, collaborate with HVAC and other home services professionals to build great brands and help them grow. We believe that not only does our company culture directly impact the lives of our employees, but it has a profound impact on the quality of work we provide to our clients.  People who enjoy working hard in a fast-paced, remote environment will thrive here. Being able to work under pressure but also knowing when to ask for help are necessary skills. At the end of the work week, you should be able to feel a sense of satisfaction because you know you worked hard as part of a supportive, creative team and that you made a difference by helping our clients move their business forward.  What BxB Media Has To Offer / Benefits  Health insurance Blue Cross / Blue Shield 100% paid of the basic plan for the employee, 4 plans availableVision and dental insurance, 50% paid for employees13 days paid time off (104 hours)6 paid holidays401K with up to 4% match, eligible after year 1Short and long-term disability$20, 000 Term life insurance benefitsEligible to add group life and accidental insurance  Job Title: Web Developer  Location: Fully Remote  Pay Rate: $50, 000 - $60, 000 a year, depending on experience  Work Schedule: Monday through Friday, 8:00 am - 5:00 pm  Job Summary: The Web Developer role is responsible for building and maintaining client websites. The Development department focuses on lev