INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (264, 'Front End Developer', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-02 09:32:22', 'LISTED', 'Zephyrus Engineering Limited is a leader in delivering high-impact engineering and technology solutions across structural engineering, architectural services, civil engineering, surveying, and forensic analysis. Our commitment to innovation and excellence drives us to advance infrastructure while promoting sustainability. Supported by a team of highly skilled professionals, Zephyrus Engineering Limited upholds the highest standards of quality across all our projects.  Position: Remote Full Stack Developer  Location: United States (Remote)  Employment Type: Full-Time  Job Overview  Zephyrus Engineering Limited is seeking an experienced and proactive Remote Full Stack Developer to join our team. As a key player in our technology division, you''ll develop and maintain web applications that support and enhance our engineering solutions. Working alongside a multidisciplinary team, you''ll be responsible for building seamless and scalable applications that optimize our operations and enrich user experiences.  Key Responsibilities  Full Stack Development:   Design, develop, and maintain high-performance web applications using modern frameworks. Work closely with UX/UI designers to implement intuitive, user-centered interfaces. Build and maintain RESTful APIs and integrate third-party services for enhanced functionality.   Database Management:   Design and manage SQL and NoSQL databases, ensuring integrity and accessibility. Optimize database performance and structure for efficiency and scalability.   Testing and Quality Assurance:   Write and execute automated tests, and conduct code reviews to uphold code quality. Identify and resolve issues swiftly to maintain a smooth, error-free user experience.   Collaboration and Communication:   Collaborate with project managers, engineers, and other stakeholders to gather and fulfill project requirements. Engage in agile 