lexibility.Ability to work extended hours and weekends as an on-call engineer TravelThis position requires domestic travel for AURA’s all-staff quarterly planning meetings and may also require some domestic travel based on business needs. Additional Eligibility Qualifications Must be able to get a background check and drug test.Work Authorization  Must be a US Citizen.Ability to obtain a Secret clearance', 'https://www.linkedin.com/job-apply/4059207263', 194, 1);
