INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (322, 'Senior Backend Developer', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-06 16:15:05', 'LISTED', 'SQA Group is excited to partner with one of our key clients to enhance their technology solutions, and we''re searching for a talented Senior Backend Software Developer to join this dynamic environment. This role requires strong skills in C# and .NET (versions 6-8) for developing, deploying, and managing backend systems within Azure’s cloud infrastructure. Familiarity with Kubernetes (AKS) is a strong plus. Key Responsibilities/Critical Success Factors:C# .NET Expertise: Develop and optimize backend applications using C# and .NET (versions 6-8), ensuring high performance and reliability.Azure Cloud Experience: Apply in-depth Azure Cloud service knowledge to build scalable, secure backend solutions within a cloud environment.Problem-Solving and Timely Delivery: Address complex technical challenges with effective solutions, consistently meeting project timelines and quality standards.Azure Service Bus Management: Configure and handle integration and messaging solutions through Azure Service Bus.Azure AI Services Utilization: Enhance application features and automate tasks using Azure AI Services, including Document Intelligence.API Development: Build and maintain backend APIs to ensure seamless system interaction and integration. Soft Skills:Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams. Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities. Self-motivated and capable of working independently as well as part of a team. Ability to manage multiple tasks and meet deadlines in a fast-paced environment. **Please note: this is a long-term consulting opportunity. Thank you for your interest in working with SQA Group. SQA Group is an equal opportunity employer and supports workforce diversity. This job description is intended to describe the general nature and level of work being performed by