INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (395, 'Remote Prompt Engineer', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-11 17:04:25', 'LISTED', 'Want to learn more about this role and Jobot? Click our Jobot logo and follow our LinkedIn page!  Job details  This Jobot Job is hosted by Conner Ferguson  Are you a fit? Easy Apply now by clicking the "Easy Apply" button and sending us your resume.  Salary $100, 000 - $140, 000 per year  A Bit About Us  We are looking for a dynamic and innovative Remote Prompt Engineer to join our team. This is an exciting opportunity for a seasoned professional to leverage their skills and experience in a fast-paced, technology-driven environment. The successful candidate will utilize their expertise in Prompt Engineering, AI, AWS, LLMs, Gemini, Llama, Claude, Python, Golang, Ruby, PHP, JavaScript, Python Scripts, One-Shot Learning, and Chain of Thought Reasoning to design, develop, and implement cutting-edge APIs.    Why join us?   Fully Remote  Health Insurance  Dental Insurance  Paid Time Off  401k  Job Details  Responsibilities   Leverage your deep understanding of Prompt, AI, and ChatGPT to develop and implement innovative tech solutions. Utilize your expertise in LLMs, Gemini, Llama, and Claude to optimize our tech services. Apply your skills in Python, Golang, Ruby, PHP, JavaScript, and Python Scripts to write robust and efficient code. Use your knowledge of One-Shot Learning and Chain of Thought Reasoning to develop and implement algorithms that drive our tech services. Design, develop, and manage APIs that facilitate seamless integration of our tech services. Collaborate with cross-functional teams to understand their needs and develop tech solutions that address these needs. Stay abreast of the latest developments in the tech services industry and leverage this knowledge to improve our services. Troubleshoot and resolve any technical issues that may arise.  Qualifications   A Bachelor''s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or a related field.