INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (415, 'Founding Software Engineer', true, 'Remote', '2024-10-30 13:21:31', 'LISTED', 'Are you interested in building fintech platforms that will transform the industry?Do you thrive in an early-stage, high-impact environment?Ready to innovate with a specialized LLM-driven platform? We''re working with a fast-growing, pre-seed fintech start-up building an LLM platform for the financial world. Their core product is an advanced assistant that empowers users to discover, create, and automate a wide range of financial tasks with remarkable accuracy. With benchmarked precision three times greater than ChatGPT, their tool is revolutionizing advanced market research, data integration, reporting, and analysis. ResponsibilitiesLead full-stack development and platform infrastructure (Python, Typescript, React)Take ownership of end-to-end features across the stack, managing all phases from concept to deploymentImplement data orchestration and cloud solutions to scale platform capabilitiesIntegrate real-world user feedback to continuously improve product effectivenessCollaborate closely with a small, dynamic team of experts, including CTO and CEO Requirements3-5+ years of full-stack experience with expertise in Python and JavaScriptProficiency with cloud platforms and deployment best practicesAbility to work autonomously and thrive in a fast-paced start-up environmentStrong problem-solving skills, particularly in data-centric applicationsExperience collaborating across functions to adapt products based on user needs Please apply if interested. Big Cloud is a leading recruiter in the AI & Data Science space. We''re lucky enough to recruit the best candidates in partnership with some of the most exciting companies all over the world. We try to reply to all applications, but we’re only human, for now! So, you may only hear from us if you are successful. Check out our latest vacancies to see what else we’re recruiting for: www.bigcloud.global/find-a-