INSERT INTO public."Jobs" VALUES (484, 'AI & Data Science Traning & Intern', true, 'Remote', '2024-11-12 18:00:08', 'LISTED', 'Refonte AI - Global Innovators in IT and Ed-Tech SolutionsRefonte AI is a globally recognized leader in IT and Ed-tech, known for excellence in artificial intelligence, digital marketing, data science, analytics, UI/UX design, web, and app development. Our mission is to drive innovation and empower talent across the world. Learn More & Apply: https://refontelearning.com Position: AI, Data Science, DevOps, and Cloud Intern Location: Remote (United States) About the Internship:Join an exciting journey in our AI, Data Science, DevOps, and Cloud Internship, designed to provide hands-on experience in these cutting-edge fields. This opportunity allows you to work on impactful projects that drive real-world solutions, helping you grow as you collaborate with a team of experienced professionals in a supportive, global environment. Program Overview:Refonte AI is looking for driven individuals to join our comprehensive AI & Data Science Internship Program. This program blends hands-on project experience with structured learning, enabling participants to develop expertise from the ground up in AI and data science.Through RGTIP (Refonte Global Training & Internship Program), you’ll collaborate on global projects, working with teams from Oceania, Asia, Europe, and the Americas—all within a flexible, remote setting. Role Responsibilities:Collaborate with multi-functional teams to create, deploy, and maintain AI-powered solutions.Gather, clean, and analyze datasets, deriving actionable insights.Assist in developing scalable data pipelines for model training and deployment.Help integrate machine learning models into production environments using DevOps methodologies.Support CI/CD pipeline design and optimization for AI applications on cloud platforms.Configure, monitor, and manage cloud infrastructure with platforms like AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud.Work with data scientists and engineers to translate business needs into technical solutions.Explore emerging tech in AI, Data Science, DevOps, and Cloud, contributing to our innovation pipeline.Collaborate on documentation efforts for effective knowledge-sharing across teams. Projects You’ll Contribute To:Multi-Cloud AI Infrastructure: Configuration, automation, and deployment for robust AI applications.Full Stack AI DevOps & Development: Hands-on experience with end-to-end AI solution development.Generative AI and Large Language Models: Work on AI models transforming text, images, audio, and video inputs into dynamic outputs.Fraud Detection Algorithms: Apply AI techniques to identify fraud patterns in financial data.Recommender Systems: Develop personalized recommendation algorithms enhancing user experience.Sentiment Analysis: Derive sentiment insights from textual data for better user sentiment understanding.Chatbot Development: Advance intelligent chatbot systems to transform customer service and interactions.Multimedia Classification: Work with image, audio, and video classification technologies.Text Analysis: Reveal patterns in textual data with advanced analytics methods. Qualifications:Current enrollment in a degree program, showing a strong commitment to continuous learning.Excellent communication skills for effective collaboration.Proven ability to work independently and as part of a dynamic team. Perks of Joining Refonte:Gain real-world experience with emerging technologies in AI, Data Science, DevOps, and Cloud.Work on meaningful projects that contribute to the tech landscape.Flexible, remote position based in Australia, connecting you with a global network. Important Information:This is an unpaid study and internship program, aimed at skill-building and professional development. Our team will follow up with application details after you apply. Learn More & Apply: https://refontelearning.com Location: Remote (United States)', 'https://www.linkedin.com/job-apply/4075008967', 57, 1);
